title: #92Noon! Warren/Russo/Lavelle/Talkers
description: Big 10 Commish Kevin Warren joins for two segments to begin the show! Then it's Michael Russo with updates on the NHL and the tricky task of restarting the league. Lavelle with more updates on baseball, and more!
